<AbstractNarration>This proposal will establish an advanced network connection from the University of the South, through Vanderbilt University to the Southern Crossroads Gigapop and on to the Abilene/Internet2 network for research and education.  Driving collaborative research applications include&lt;br/&gt;* Landscape analysis&lt;br/&gt;* Appalachian Watershed Research,&lt;br/&gt;* GIS Information for the Cumberland Plateau, and &lt;br/&gt;* Astronomy to share research data.&lt;br/&gt;</AbstractNarration>
